## TECHNOLOGY OVERVIEW

### Agent Platform (Built)
- **Frontend:** React 18, Tailwind CSS, Shadcn UI
- **Backend:** FastAPI (Python), ~1,900 lines server
- **Database:** MongoDB (provisioned, currently JSON files â€” migration planned)
- **AI:** OpenAI GPT-4o integration for image analysis and data extraction
- **Email Generation:** Custom HTML generator with 4 template types, 11 modular generator files
- **CRM:** Full pipeline (Inquiry > Quoted > Booked > Traveled > Inactive)
- **Invoicing:** CRUD with payment status tracking, PDF export
- **Client Portal:** Shareable public links with view tracking
- **Calendar:** Google, Outlook, Yahoo, ICS integration

### Referral Hub (Built)
- **Platform:** WordPress Plugin v3.0.1
- **Auth:** Session-based with 24-hour timeout
- **Dashboard:** 5 tabs (Home, Dashboard, Handbook, Benefits, Payment)
- **Signup:** Multi-step quiz (5 questions) + application form
- **Mock Data:** Development system ready for production data sources

